{"tid":998162,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［認真 求吊醒］人生無咩目標 求吊醒","createTime":"2019-01-27T18:04:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T14:54:45.000Z","uid":207711,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9b3a5bda18b145a3688f367deaf6e52f35c4e00f","tid":998162,"uid":207711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T18:04:01.000Z","msg":"細細個嗰陣 有好多目標 好多都做到<br />\n玩下運動 比下賽 攞下獎咁<br />\n反而畢業之後冇曬目標 變左廢青<br />\n.<br />\n畢左業兩年 讀緊asso <br />\n星期一至五讀書 六日走去飲酒<br />\n有時間就考下啲牌<br />\n畢左業兩年同岩岩畢業一樣 混混惡惡<br />\n搵唔到一條想走既路<br />\n人生冇意義<br />\n<br />\n利申：知自己廢 屌還屌幫小弟諗下有咩人生意義 可以追求啲咩"},{"pid":"68b33bb37ba215922a835eba21b463254640019f","tid":998162,"uid":207711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T18:06:44.000Z","msg":"連登大大們比啲意見😢"},{"pid":"496825b92fa160483cac5157e1a182ef3d3af5de","tid":998162,"uid":75790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T18:11:05.000Z","msg":"九月報小一開學囉"},{"pid":"6259b1bbf2634d53e6752c41eeef2ee9b992b5b7","tid":998162,"uid":72531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T18:11:47.000Z","msg":"咁你姐係已經u grad定仲讀緊asso<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f07df3035a42a5d7db7265151be742f1f740a6d","tid":998162,"uid":207711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"496825b92fa160483cac5157e1a182ef3d3af5de","tid":998162,"uid":75790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T18:11:05.000Z","msg":"九月報小一開學囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T18:12:47.000Z","msg":"準備嫁喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1071f0e6a31c068a31aa7056d1273f567b7f58fe","tid":998162,"uid":207711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6259b1bbf2634d53e6752c41eeef2ee9b992b5b7","tid":998162,"uid":72531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T18:11:47.000Z","msg":"咁你姐係已經u grad定仲讀緊asso<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"